WITH THOSE STATUES

32:38.780 --> 32:40.361
AND GOD KNOWS WHAT ELSE.

32:40.400 --> 32:44.188
BUT THE POINT IS JUST YOU
AND ME SPENDING SOME...

32:49.720 --> 32:54.373
OH, ZEEK.

32:54.420 --> 32:55.682
