32:55.730 --> 33:01.077
YEAH.

33:01.110 --> 33:05.183
WELL, WE COULD STILL GO.
CAN'T WE?

33:05.220 --> 33:07.188
I MEAN,
AFTER YOU SEE LELAND,

33:07.220 --> 33:08.733
HE OKAYS YOU FOR YOUR TRAVEL,

33:08.770 --> 33:11.352
WE'LL JUST GO.

33:11.400 --> 33:13.800
