SOMETHING ABOUT IT OR NOT.

39:06.890 --> 39:11.850
YOU KNOW, ONE GIRL WITH FLAMES
FOR HAIR.

39:11.900 --> 39:13.060
WHAT IS THAT?

39:13.100 --> 39:17.935
HEY.

39:17.970 --> 39:21.861
YOU ASKED ME IF I'M HAPPY.

39:21.910 --> 39:24.799
I'M HAPPY.

39:24.840 --> 39:29.868
THERE'S NOWHERE ELSE
I WANT TO BE.

39:29.910 --> 39:32.151
