39:58.010 --> 39:59.898
WE NEED TO SIGN
THE PAPERS, JOEL.

39:59.940 --> 40:01.498
WE MADE A DECISION.

40:01.530 --> 40:03.634
WE NEED TO FOLLOW
THROUGH WITH IT.

40:03.670 --> 40:08.562
- JULIA--
- ENOUGH SECOND GUESSING.

